Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMBitmapSquareHK-Light\fs45\bord0\shad0\b1\pos(696,910)}松永七段出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMBitmapSquareHK-Light\fs30\bord0\shad0\b1\pos(1242,223)}戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMBitmapSquareHK-Light\fs30\bord0\shad0\b1\pos(1462.5,221.5)}作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMBitmapSquareHK-Light\fs30\bord0\shad0\b1\pos(1243.5,293.5)}保命
